statements: SELECT * FROM IdentityTheftDetection;
SELECT name, address, credit_score FROM IdentityTheftDetection WHERE credit_score > 700;
SELECT id, name, social_security_number FROM IdentityTheftDetection WHERE name LIKE 'A%';
SELECT * FROM IdentityTheftDetection ORDER BY credit_score DESC;
SELECT name, machine_learning_algorithm_used FROM IdentityTheftDetection WHERE address LIKE '%Street%';
SELECT id, name, address, social_security_number, credit_score, machine_learning_algorithm_used FROM IdentityTheftDetection WHERE credit_score > 700 ORDER BY name DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM IdentityTheftDetection WHERE address LIKE '%Street%' AND credit_score BETWEEN 600 AND 800 ORDER BY credit_score ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT id, name, social_security_number FROM IdentityTheftDetection WHERE machine_learning_algorithm_used = 'Random Forest' ORDER BY id ASC, credit_score DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT id, name, credit_score FROM IdentityTheftDetection WHERE social_security_number LIKE '123%' ORDER BY credit_score DESC, id ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM IdentityTheftDetection WHERE credit_score < 500 OR credit_score > 800 ORDER BY credit_score DESC, id DESC LIMIT 5;
